# Copy to .dev.vars (gitignored). Only add what you need.

# --- Filter (optional) — same format as Cloudflare Dashboard ---
# IMPORTANT: One line = one value. JSON with commas breaks .dev.vars unless quoted:
# FILTER_CLICKBAIT_PATTERNS="[\"網民\",\"網友\",\"被指\"]"
# Or use comma-separated (no brackets):
# FILTER_CLICKBAIT_PATTERNS=網民,網友,被指
# FILTER_EXCLUDE_KEYWORDS=keyword1,keyword2

# --- Below: optional unless you use those features locally ---

# Crawl API (Jetso Today / Uniqlo / Mannings etc.): only if you trigger crawl on local dev.
# Leave empty if you only use RSS + direct fetch sources + ingest script.
# CF_ACCOUNT_ID=
# CF_API_TOKEN=

# If unset: /api/ingest, /api/refresh, /api/purge-excluded need no Bearer header locally.
# REFRESH_SECRET=
